{"tid":2419648,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★滙豐復派息　麥玲玲稱心情會「好返啲」","createTime":"2021-02-23T11:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T12:23:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"749ccf982212a5049dc638a47cbb1cd2ed19721c","tid":2419648,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"麥玲玲感慨，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>以前的前輩教落，有錢就要買滙豐</strong></span>，但自己其實又沒有刻意好活躍去買，笑言自己純粹「買咗嚟擺」，本身亦沒有在股票市場上活躍，並且有其他公用股去收息，所以只會繼續「揸住佢」，不甚理會股價高低。<br />\n<br />\n對於今次業績能夠重派股息，麥玲玲坦言是正面，「因為有不少老人家及退休人士都在等派息，部分更是他們的收入，所以上年沒有息派大家當然不會高興，但相信經過今日，大家的心情都會『好返啲』！」她補充道，加上最近債息上升對銀行股有利，有不少利好因素出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/專題人訪/590917/滙豐復派息-麥玲玲稱心情會-好返啲-籲留心偏財星衝撃股市\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%A8%AA%2F590917%2F%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E5%BE%A9%E6%B4%BE%E6%81%AF-%E9%BA%A5%E7%8E%B2%E7%8E%B2%E7%A8%B1%E5%BF%83%E6%83%85%E6%9C%83-%E5%A5%BD%E8%BF%94%E5%95%B2-%E7%B1%B2%E7%95%99%E5%BF%83%E5%81%8F%E8%B2%A1%E6%98%9F%E8%A1%9D%E6%92%83%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv34jkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=d34f9080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/專題人訪/590917/滙豐復派息-麥玲玲稱心情會-好返啲-籲留心偏財星衝撃股市</a>"},{"pid":"41508910df0ad1a8d6112a5b704986f8594ec84d","tid":2419648,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:54:13.000Z","msg":"聽從廢老言，乞米在眼前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">以前的前輩教落，有錢就要買滙豐</span>"},{"pid":"d1f68236a1eae5918854ff67ddae2b9232ea17dc","tid":2419648,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:55:03.000Z","msg":"等睇樓主匯豐廣告gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class